<db:para>QChart class provides two methods that map between the scene coordinates and the series domain (defined by the axes ranges).</db:para>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> QChart::mapToPosition(const <db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> &amp;value, QAbstractSeries *series)</db:para>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> QChart::mapToValue(const <db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> &amp;position, QAbstractSeries *series)</db:para>
